he timescales\nwe observe and thus may be the dominant source of H$\\alpha$ variability on\nactive fully-convective M dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2022 19:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
