s, with nearly 85% reduction in latency. In our\nquest for efficient ML on the edge, WNNs are clearly deserving of additional\nattention.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 01:46:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-04"}
