tside for\npersistent malware, since automatic scan of an AV tool or a power cycle, like\nwe are used to for Windows malware and Mirai infections, will not solve\npersistent IoT malware infections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 12:47:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-04"}
